quran[10]{c,v,t}:
  77,41,"Mu by’ukuri, abatinya Allah (ku munsi w’imperuka) bazaba bari hagati y’ibicucu (by’ibiti byo mu ijuru) ndetse n’amasoko (atemba)"
  77,42,(Bazaba bafitemo) n’imbuto (z’amoko anyuranye) bazajya bifuza
  77,43,"(Bazabwirwa bati) \"Nimurye, munywe kandi mugubwe neza kubera ibyo mwakoze"
  77,44,"Mu by’ukuri, uko ni ko tugororera abakoze neza"
  77,45,Ibihano bikaze bizaba kuri babandi bahinyura (umunsi w’izuka)
  77,46,"(Yemwe bahakanyi) \"Nimurye munishimishe by’igihe gito (mu buzima bwo ku isi), kuko rwose muri inkozi z’ibibi"
  77,47,Ibihano bikaze bizaba kuri babandi bahinyura (umunsi w’izuka)
  77,48,"N’iyo babwiwe bati \"Nimwuname (musenge)!\" Ntabwo bunama (ngo basenge)"
  77,49,Ibihano bikaze bizaba kuri babandi bahinyura (umunsi w’izuka)
  77,50,Nonese nyuma y’iyi (Qur’an) ni ayahe magambo yandi bazemera